{"tid":1116012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【不安慎入】學生與母爭執後奪門而出跳橋輕生 母緊隨痛哭","createTime":"2019-04-19T15:23:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-21T11:44:30.000Z","uid":46488,"like":80,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"059c8eb2dfa325686afa08d764c3066448bf634b","tid":1116012,"uid":46488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:23:06.000Z","msg":"上海一名17歲少年疑因在校與同學爭執，及後遭其母批評，少年不堪受辱，周三（17日）遂在盧浦大橋突然離開私家車，並從高處跳下，其母不及抓緊對方，繼而坐地痛哭。少年最終不幸身亡，整個過程歷時不足5秒。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，該名少年就讀當地某職業學校二年級。少年母親表示，事發是周三晚上約10時，她正用座駕載着兒子上路，詎料少年突然落車並迅速跳橋。警方事後到場調查搜索，最終在橋下綠化帶內發現少年倒臥其中，及後證實身亡。 <br />\n<br />\n&darr;&darr;Video&darr;&darr;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>生仔要考牌!!</strong></div></span>"},{"pid":"bfee44703c67315f0dc8de1f598aa4ebd739d4d4","tid":1116012,"uid":59699,"like":109,"dislike":2,"score":107,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:24:13.000Z","msg":"她正用座駕載着兒子上路"},{"pid":"c390b764faafb38d27fb01603e9a9a786d16fddb","tid":1116012,"uid":112404,"like":55,"dislike":8,"score":47,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:24:37.000Z","msg":"支那人沒有一個是無辜的"},{"pid":"a17a0c60fd9f71ce5ebf989100b0d468c1df74e9","tid":1116012,"uid":34410,"like":16,"dislike":135,"score":-119,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:33:45.000Z","msg":"依家d廢青00後有冇咁廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾老母話幾句就死 有勇氣跳橋逃避現實冇勇氣面對社會"},{"pid":"a13b10942e1e6e57226693b2271e65c1cc61a350","tid":1116012,"uid":242872,"like":81,"dislike":6,"score":75,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:34:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82bf5e21ac4e8daa13162d91265e6cb2bfeabd8c","tid":1116012,"uid":165336,"like":251,"dislike":8,"score":243,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T15:36:13.000Z","msg":"肯定係俾人洽完個老母仲迫佢同人道歉<br />\n華人社會父母就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n永遠都係自己仔女錯人地仔女好"},{"pid":"c67b0bfca9eae4eb77b5eb37d5e5e62da